Hi Richard,
I thought of moving /proc/kcore to devfs and there is no obvious place to
put it. Why not create a /dev/debug/ and put kcore (and profile) in there?
In the future one can have ktrace (or whatever it was called from IKD
patches, can't remember).
What thinkest thou?
